      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Mesh convergence study must demonstrate <5% change in peak von Mises stress and construct stiffness between successive refinement levels.",
      "rationale": "Richardson extrapolation performed across three mesh refinements; stiffness GCI = 1.8%, peak stress GCI = 3.1%; both within 5% threshold."
