      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Constitutive model must capture elastic-plastic titanium alloy behavior with isotropic hardening; contact formulation must represent screw-rod interface.",
      "rationale": "Bilinear isotropic hardening plasticity calibrated to Ti-6Al-4V tensile coupon data; augmented Lagrangian contact at screw-rod and screw-block interfaces; model form validated against published literature."
    },
