      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities must employ the same device geometry, material, and loading protocol as the intended regulatory submission context.",
      "rationale": "Validation uses production-representative 7.5 mm non-cannulated pedicle screw constructs under ASTM F1717 compression-bending protocol, directly mirroring the regulatory submission test plan; two independent laboratories confirm reproducibility."
